  <description>
    <p>
      A faithful Windows 95/98 Notepad clone built with Tauri and styled with 98.css
      for an authentic retro experience.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Classic Windows 98 user interface</li>
      <li>File operations (New, Open, Save, Save As)</li>
      <li>Edit functions (Cut, Copy, Paste, Find, Replace)</li>
      <li>Word wrap toggle</li>
      <li>Font customization</li>
      <li>Dark mode support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
